================================================================
Third-party data — JMdict (Japanese-Multilingual Dictionary)
================================================================

JLPTDeck embeds entries derived from JMdict, maintained by the
Electronic Dictionary Research and Development Group (EDRDG).

JMdict is distributed under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike
4.0 International License (CC BY-SA 4.0).
  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/
  https://www.edrdg.org/jmdict/edict_doc.html

Per CC BY-SA 4.0:
  - Attribution: see in-app Settings → "데이터 출처 / 라이선스" + this LICENSE.
  - ShareAlike: derivative dictionary data shipped with this app
    (e.g., the bundled `jmdict_n4_n1.json` and any `gloss_ko` Korean
    translation field added by JLPTDeck) is also licensed under
    CC BY-SA 4.0. Anyone may redistribute the dictionary data subject
    to the same license.
  - The application source code (Swift / SwiftUI / TCA / SwiftData)
    is NOT a derivative work of the dictionary and remains under MIT.

================================================================
Third-party data — Tanos JLPT vocabulary lists
================================================================

JLPT level classification (n4 / n3 / n2 / n1) per word is sourced from
Jonathan Waller's Tanos.co.uk JLPT vocabulary lists.
  https://www.tanos.co.uk/jlpt/

These lists are unofficial estimates and are not affiliated with the
Japan Foundation, the official JLPT examination body, or the Japan
Educational Exchanges and Services. The bundled in-app Settings
screen surfaces this disclaimer; v1.0 ships with explicit
"비공식 추정" attribution.

Tanos data has been used here for non-commercial educational purposes.
A licensing inquiry was sent to the maintainer of the Tanos data on
(date pending — see PLAN.md F1). If the maintainer requests removal
or revised attribution, JLPTDeck will issue a hotfix.

